    ],

      [/./, "comment"]
    ],
    pseudoColumns: [
      [
        /[$][A-Za-z_][\w@#$]*/,
        {
          cases: {
            "@pseudoColumns": "predefined",
            "@default": "identifier"
          }
        }
      ]
    ],
    numbers: [
      [/0[xX][0-9a-fA-F]*/, "number"],
      [/[$][+-]*\d*(\.\d*)?/, "number"],
      [/((\d+(\.\d*)?)|(\.\d+))([eE][\-+]?\d+)?/, "number"]
    ],
    strings: [[/'/, { token: "string", next: "@string" }]],
    string: [
      [/[^']+/, "string"],
      [/''/, "string"],
      [/'/, { token: "string", next: "@pop" }]
    ],
    complexIdentifiers: [[/"/, { token: "identifier.quote", next: "@quotedIdentifier" }]],
    quotedIdentifier: [
      [/[^"]+/, "identifier"],
      [/""/, "identifier"],
      [/"/, { token: "identifier.quote", next: "@pop" }]
    ],
    scopes: []
  }
};
